60 determine determines and order orders that the relocation of
61 any utility facility is necessitated by the construction of
62 any project on the national system of interstate and defense
63 highways, including the extensions thereof within urban areas,
64 the utility owning or operating the utility facility shall
65 relocate the facility in accordance with the order of the
66 Director of Transportation. Notwithstanding the foregoing, if
67 the cost of the utility facility relocation is eligible and
68 approved for reimbursement by the federal government, the cost
